ology\", \"score\": 0.9999999997594387, \"rank\": 2.406003969041484e-10, \"text\": \"Greek mythology\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the God\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"celebration\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was to have a pagan celebration connected to the gods of Olympus.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.9999999993660822, \"rank\": 6.341213196398529e-10, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"a pagan celebration\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"the gods\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will never find in me a desire to mock and denigrate anyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a desire\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, the official Twitter account for the 2024 Paris Olympics also noted that it was a nod to Dionysus with the caption, \\\"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings.\\\"\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2216, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2933299820522624e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.107342008405025e-21, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999985388378024, \"rank\": 1.3863076595891888e-06, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.107342008405025e-21, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"The interpretation\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"the absurdity\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"human beings\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking withAPshortly after Friday's ceremony, Jolly addressed what the overall intent was for the ceremony without diving into the specifics of the moment in question.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday's ceremony\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall intent\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the specifics\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" Jolly shared.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During Sunday's International Olympic Committee (IOC) news conference, 2024 Paris Olympics spokespersonAnne Descampswas asked aboutthe backlash from Christians, echoing Jolly's sentiments on the matter.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2926, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8905136056058532, \"rank\": 0.11973296806947054, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Descampswas\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"aboutthe backlash\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly's sentiments\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly, there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I think [with] Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking at the results of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3331, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3288}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoyed this?\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please share on social media!\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3389}]}]}"